summary:
Makes Whiterun into a beautiful forest :)
along with a better looking Shrine to Our great Talos \"For the Stormcloaks!\"
descriptionHtml:
PLEASE LOOK IN OTHER FILES BEFORE CLICKING \"Download with mod manager\"!
Adds a more forest look to the city of whiterun, really pretty :3 even in the mornings <3. Anyways please leave suggestions and comments :) iI will try to work on Windhelm and the other cities, Most definitely Riften.
author: Mitchie22
